<L>__{interior bridge night}
<A>__{as wind and rain pummel the bridge window.. admiral robertson turns to his chief engineer.}
<C>__{admiral robertson}
<D>__{let's kick in the stablilizers, mr. carlson, and get the seas off the quarter. these kids are in for one hell of a storm.}
<C>__{chief engineer}
