<A>__{the chief engineer moves to a bank of toggle switches, flipping a row of them. tight on navigational chart wall same time as a bloodstained hand silently removes the rusty harpoon hanging above the map.}
<B>__{admiral robertson}
<A>__{gets a reflective look in his weary eyes.}
<D>__{admiral robertson how olds your boy now, carlson?}
